name: Symbiotic Presence
description:
Each time any ally within 40 yds uses an Azerite Essence, gain 7 Intellect and 4 Haste for 20 sec.

The ally who used an Azerite Essence also gains 4 Haste for 20 sec. Only one ally can have this Haste effect at a time.

Unique: Corruption Resistance increased by 10.
